trans-unit.source: Defines the methods called during contract generation that can be used to modify the generated code for a service contract.
trans-unit.target: Definierar metoder anropas under generering av kontrakt som kan användas för att ändra den genererade koden för ett servicekontrakt.

trans-unit.source: Implement the IServiceContractGenerationExtension interface on a contract behavior (a <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName> type) to enable you to modify the code generated when a contract or endpoint is compiled into code.
trans-unit.target: Implementera gränssnittet IServiceContractGenerationExtension på ett beteende för kontrakt (en <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>typ) så att du kan ändra den kod som skapas när ett kontrakt eller en slutpunkt kompileras i kod.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IContractBehavior?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Typically, a custom <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> inserts a custom contract behavior into the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection during the call to <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Normalt en anpassad <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>infogar ett anpassat kontraktet beteende i <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen under anropet till <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A>eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportEndpoint%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension.ImportContract%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ContractDescription.Behaviors%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Implement to modify the code document object model prior to the contract generation process.
trans-unit.target: Implementera om du vill ändra koden document object model innan generation kontraktet.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName> to modify the contract, operations, or the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName> prior to code generation.
trans-unit.target: Använd den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName>att ändra kontraktet, åtgärder eller <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName>innan kodgenerering.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceContractGenerationContext?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The code generated context to use to modify the code document prior to generation.
trans-unit.target: Koden genereras kontext för att använda för att ändra koden dokumentet före generering.
